{
  "id": "api/core/OnChanges",
  "title": "OnChanges",
  "contents": "\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/metadata/lifecycle_hooks.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L22-L60\" aria-label=\"建议修改\" title=\"建议修改\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.1.0/packages/core/src/metadata/lifecycle_hooks.ts#L22-L60\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n    <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n      {\n        \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n        \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n        \"itemListElement\": [\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/core/OnChanges\", \"name\": \"OnChanges\" } }\n        ]\n      }\n    </script>\n      <a href=\"/api\">API</a> / <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"onchanges\">OnChanges<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/OnChanges#onchanges\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label interface\">interface</label>\n    \n    \n    <label class=\"api-status-label stable\">稳定</label>\n    \n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <p class=\"short-description\"></p><p translation-origin=\"off\">A lifecycle hook that is called when any data-bound property of a directive changes.\nDefine an <code>ngOnChanges()</code> method to handle the changes.</p>\n<p translation-result=\"\">一个生命周期钩子，当指令的任何一个可绑定属性发生变化时调用。\n定义一个 <code>ngOnChanges()</code> 方法来处理这些变更。</p>\n<p></p>\n  \n\n  \n\n  <section class=\"interface-overview\">\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\">\ninterface <a href=\"api/core/OnChanges\" class=\"code-anchor\">OnChanges</a> {\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/OnChanges#ngOnChanges\">ngOnChanges(changes: SimpleChanges): void</a>\n}\n</code-example>\n\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \n  <div class=\"descendants class\">\n    <h2 id=\"实现类\">实现类<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/OnChanges#实现类\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    \n\n<ul>\n  \n    <li>\n      <code><a href=\"api/upgrade/static/UpgradeComponent\" class=\"code-anchor\">UpgradeComponent</a></code>\n      \n\n\n    </li>\n  \n</ul>\n\n\n  </div>\n  \n\n</section>\n\n  \n<section class=\"see-also\">\n  <h2 id=\"see-also\">参见<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/OnChanges#see-also\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n  \n    <li><p translation-origin=\"off\"><code><a href=\"api/core/DoCheck\" class=\"code-anchor\">DoCheck</a></code></p>\n</li>\n    <li><p translation-origin=\"off\"><code><a href=\"api/core/OnInit\" class=\"code-anchor\">OnInit</a></code></p>\n</li>\n    <li><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/lifecycle-hooks#onchanges\">Lifecycle Hooks</a> guide</p>\n<p translation-result=\"\"><a href=\"guide/lifecycle-hooks#onchanges\">生命周期钩子</a></p>\n</li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n\n  \n  \n\n  \n\n\n  \n\n<section class=\"instance-methods\">\n  <h2 id=\"方法\">方法<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/OnChanges#方法\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  \n    <a id=\"ngOnChanges\"></a>\n<table class=\"is-full-width method-table instance-method\">\n  <thead><tr><th>\n    <div class=\"with-github-links\">\n      <h3 id=\"ngonchanges\">\n        ngOnChanges()\n        \n      <a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/OnChanges#ngonchanges\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n      <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/metadata/lifecycle_hooks.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L47-L59\" aria-label=\"建议修改\" title=\"建议修改\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.1.0/packages/core/src/metadata/lifecycle_hooks.ts#L47-L59\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n    </div>\n  </th></tr></thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"short-description\">\n        <p translation-origin=\"off\">A callback method that is invoked immediately after the\ndefault change detector has checked data-bound properties\nif at least one has changed, and before the view and content\nchildren are checked.</p>\n<p translation-result=\"\">如果至少发生了一次变更，则该回调方法会在默认的变更检测器检查完可绑定属性之后、视图子节点和内容子节点检查完之前调用。</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        \n\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" linenums=\"false\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">ngOnChanges(<a href=\"api/core/QueryList#changes\" class=\"code-anchor\">changes</a>: <a href=\"api/core/SimpleChanges\" class=\"code-anchor\">SimpleChanges</a>): void</code-example>\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"参数\">参数</h4>\n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table instance-method-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n  \n    <tr class=\"instance-method-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>changes</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n      <p translation-origin=\"off\">The changed properties.</p>\n<p translation-result=\"\">那些发生了变化的属性。</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"返回值\">返回值</h4>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\"><code>void</code></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n    </tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n</section>\n\n\n  \n<section class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">使用说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/OnChanges#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p translation-origin=\"off\">The following snippet shows how a component can implement this interface to\ndefine an on-changes handler for an input property.</p>\n<p translation-result=\"\">下列代码片段展示了组件要如何实现本接口来定义一个输入属性的变更处理器。</p>\n<code-example>\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({selector: 'my-cmp', <a href=\"api/core/Component#template\" class=\"code-anchor\">template</a>: `...`})\nclass MyComponent implements <a href=\"api/core/OnChanges\" class=\"code-anchor\">OnChanges</a> {\n  // TODO(issue/24571): remove '!'.\n  @<a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a>()\n  prop !: number;\n\n  ngOnChanges(<a href=\"api/core/QueryList#changes\" class=\"code-anchor\">changes</a>: <a href=\"api/core/SimpleChanges\" class=\"code-anchor\">SimpleChanges</a>) {\n    // changes.prop contains the old and the new value...\n  }\n}\n\n</code-example>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common/NgComponentOutlet\n - api/common/NgTemplateOutlet\n - api/core\n - api/core/DoCheck\n - api/core/SimpleChanges\n - api/forms/FormControlDirective\n - api/forms/FormControlName\n - api/forms/FormGroupDirective\n - api/forms/MaxLengthValidator\n - api/forms/MinLengthValidator\n - api/forms/NgModel\n - api/forms/PatternValidator\n - api/router/RouterLinkActive\n - api/router/RouterLinkWithHref\n - api/upgrade/static/UpgradeComponent\n - guide/component-interaction\n - guide/lifecycle-hooks\n - guide/styleguide\n - guide/testing\n - guide/upgrade\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/Component#template\n - api/core/DoCheck\n - api/core/Input\n - api/core/OnChanges#ngOnChanges\n - api/core/OnChanges#ngonchanges\n - api/core/OnChanges#onchanges\n - api/core/OnChanges#see-also\n - api/core/OnChanges#usage-notes\n - api/core/OnChanges#实现类\n - api/core/OnChanges#方法\n - api/core/OnInit\n - api/core/QueryList#changes\n - api/core/SimpleChanges\n - api/upgrade/static/UpgradeComponent\n - guide/lifecycle-hooks#onchanges\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/metadata/lifecycle_hooks.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L22-L60\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/metadata/lifecycle_hooks.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L47-L59\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.1.0/packages/core/src/metadata/lifecycle_hooks.ts#L22-L60\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.1.0/packages/core/src/metadata/lifecycle_hooks.ts#L47-L59\n-->"
